629
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:51,700
What's there to be afraid of?

630
00:29:52,900 --> 00:29:54,500
Let the young ones

631
00:29:54,740 --> 00:29:56,660
deal with the new problem.

632
00:29:57,180 --> 00:29:58,260
If they can't,

633
00:29:58,980 --> 00:30:00,540
