685
00:31:51,220 --> 00:31:52,340
But there was this one thing

686
00:31:52,420 --> 00:31:53,180
that left

687
00:31:53,660 --> 00:31:54,660
quite the impression.

688
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:04,940
Is this the Freedom Formidable Fist?

689
00:32:04,940 --> 00:32:06,420
[Religious Disciplines]

690
00:32:06,860 --> 00:32:07,780
Wuxin.

691
00:32:08,420 --> 00:32:10,740
But gods and demons.

692
00:32:10,940 --> 00:32:13,700
Who decides which is which?

693
00:32:17,180 --> 00:32:18,500
I don't know.

694
00:32:18,820 --> 00:32:20,300
If Master says it's a demon,

695
00:32:20,340 --> 00:32:21,780
then I'll kill it.

696
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:23,740
The scripture says

697
00:32:24,020 --> 00:32:27,300
to eliminate demons
is to eliminate the source of worries.

698
00:32:27,540 --> 00:32:30,220
What should be eliminated
is not the external threat

699
00:32:30,220 --> 00:32:32,340
but the inner demon.

700
00:32:33,860 --> 00:32:35,020
If you hadn't told me in person,

701
00:32:35,860 --> 00:32:37,060
I wouldn't believe

702
00:32:37,340 --> 00:32:38,420
that came from

703
