712
00:32:56,340 --> 00:32:58,100
When I turned 17, I went to Xueyue City

713
00:32:58,420 --> 00:32:59,300
to study under Master,

714
00:32:59,740 --> 00:33:00,820
and now, it's been six years.

715
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:02,660
The past 23 years

716
00:33:03,300 --> 00:33:04,020
feel like

717
00:33:04,220 --> 00:33:05,140
