788
00:38:36,620 --> 00:38:37,580
Master.

789
00:38:40,180 --> 00:38:41,020
Weep no more.

790
00:38:42,260 --> 00:38:44,940
You shall return to your home.

791
00:38:47,220 --> 00:38:50,260
My home is Hanshui Temple.

792
00:38:50,980 --> 00:38:54,260
[Hanshui Temple]

793
00:38:54,300 --> 00:38:56,220
This is Hanshui Temple.

794
00:38:56,780 --> 00:38:59,540
Your home, from now on.

795
00:39:10,020 --> 00:39:11,980
